ED_Title: Observer status for the International  Parliamentarians’ Congress in the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 45th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2023, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Sixth Committee, (A/78/456, para.8.)  decided to defer a decision on the request for observer status for the International Parliamentarians’ Congress in the General Assembly (Footnote: See A/78/141.)  until the seventy-ninth session of the Assembly.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
